242. Valid Anagram
Solution Link: https://leetcode.com/problems/valid-anagram/discuss/2344569/simple-c-3-lines-solution-easy-to-understand


We can simply sort both the strings and just compare whether they are equal or not.

class Solution {
public:
    bool isAnagram(string s, string t) {
        sort(s.begin(), s.end());
        sort(t.begin(), t.end());
        return s==t;
    }
};

